    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older fair-condition example that presents as a usable driver, but not a show car. Expect visible cosmetic wear, age-related blemishes, and an interior that shows use, though it remains serviceable overall. This is the kind of car for someone who wants an honest driver with imperfections rather than a fully sorted, collector-grade example. Priced accordingly for its condition.",
