      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Honest project or fixer-upper being sold in poor condition. This car shows significant wear and age, and while it may still have some usable parts or potential for someone willing to put in the work, buyers should expect cosmetic issues, mechanical needs, and overall signs of neglect or heavy use. Best suited for someone looking for a restoration candidate, a parts car, or an inexpensive project rather than a ready-to-drive example.",
