      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone looking for inexpensive transportation without unnecessary frills. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a solid opportunity for a handy buyer, commuter, or anyone needing an affordable daily driver. Priced to reflect its condition and deliver strong value, this is a chance to get on the road for less.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car you can put to work right away or turn into a rewarding little project? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. A great fit for someone who wants simple transportation without spending a fortune, or for a handy owner who enjoys bringing a car back to its best. Priced fairly and presented straight \u2014 come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right match for you.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of upside for the next owner. Engine starts, runs, and pulls well, transmission does its job, and the chassis feels like a good candidate for someone who wants an inexpensive platform to sort, tune, or use as a dependable around-town car. Not a cosmetic queen and it shows its age, but it has the kind of honest, usable character that makes sense for a hands-on buyer. If you want affordable entry with real potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car right now. Rough around the edges, priced to move, and worth a look if you want basic transportation without the big bill.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn personality you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its panels and plenty of charm left to give. It\u2019s an ideal pick for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly ride with character, whether you\u2019re after a practical runabout, a project with potential, or simply dependable transportation with a little grit and soul. A chance to own something affordable, approachable, and full of possibility.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with solid value for the price. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer seeking a low-cost daily driver, project car, or dependable backup option. It shows its age and is being offered as-is, but it remains a practical opportunity to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point. Priced to sell and worth a look for anyone who appreciates honest value.",
      "price": 4950.0,
